🌟 GitHub Profile Generator



Create stunning GitHub profile READMEs in seconds with this interactive Streamlit app featuring glassmorphism design.

## ✨ Features
- 🎨 **Glassmorphism UI** - Beautiful blurred background effect
- 📝 **Customizable Templates** - Simple or Professional styles
- 🛠️ **Tech Stack Badges** - 20+ technologies with auto-generated badges
- 📊 **GitHub Stats** - Automatic stats, streaks, and language cards
- 🐍 **Snake Animation** - Optional contribution graph animation
- 📲 **Social Links** - All your important profiles in one place

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Run Locally
```bash
pip install streamlit
streamlit run profile_generator.py
Run in Google Colab
Open in Colab

